  <name>HashVerifier</name>
  <summary>Checksum generation and verification</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Cross-platform checksum generation and verification tool with CLI and GTK3 GUI.
      Features recursive directory hashing, file verification, real-time progress tracking,
      and support for symbolic links.
    </p>
    <p>
      Supports 11 hash algorithms: CRC32, MD4, MD5, SHA1, SHA256, SHA384, SHA512,
      SHA3-256, SHA3-384, SHA3-512, and BLAKE3.
    </p>
  </description>
